Sentencas: Porous thick films of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (LSCF) on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (CGO) substrates were prepared by the electrophoretic deposition (EPD) method.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)

Sentencas: Organic suspensions of different compositions containing LSCF ceramic particles were investigated with the aim to determine the optimal composition of the suspension and EPD conditions.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)

Sentencas: Stainless steel substrates were used in order to determine the optimal parameters for the EPD process.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)

Sentencas: The best results were achieved with solutions containing acetylacetone, iodine and starch.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)

Sentencas: The EPD conditions leading to uniform LSCF films were: applied voltage 20 V and deposition time 120 s, with the electrodes separated 1.5 cm.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)

Sentencas: EPD was also demonstrated to be a simple and useful method for making porous LSCF cathodes on CGO substrates.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)

Sentencas: It was shown that the microstructure of the films can be controlled by changing the applied voltage, deposition time and concentration of additives in suspension.
Titulo: Electrophoretic deposition of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathodes on Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 substrates for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC)
